name: Sharklab 1
description:
Sharklab 1 is the first of a series of animated gifs about a not so distant future when humans are still trying to preserve shark species to help them build a new world.

This series of PC-produced 3D-animated works portray a variety of bases with different rarities. Extra features will be uncovered later on.

Planet: Earth
Base: Iceland
Lab Workers: 6
Spaceship: None
Lab Code: Hidden
